<br>
One thing though - I've found out through experience that it's a bad idea to attach numbers to the ideas you propose, even as examples, in public forums like this. The discussion will turn from your idea to debating the numbers, and the thread gets derailed fast. (I bet at least a few people read this post and wanted to post a comment on the stats on the badge of ordination)<br>
<br>
A server-changing event that people would be happy about, that they accomplished through collective effort, seems like a pretty positive thing.<br>
